      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Here's a great opportunity to own a dependable, well-maintained vehicle that's ready to hit the road! This car is in genuinely good condition \u2014 the paint looks solid with only minor signs of everyday use, the interior is clean and comfortable, and the mechanicals are in good working order. It's not showroom-perfect, but it's the kind of reliable, honest used car that delivers real value without surprises. Come take a look \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
