    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but shows visible wear consistent with its age and mileage \u2014 expect minor dents, scratches, and some fading on the exterior. The interior shows normal use wear. Mechanically it is functional, though some maintenance items may be due. No major mechanical failures, but this is not a like-new vehicle.",
