    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well with no significant mechanical issues. There is normal wear consistent with its age, and minor cosmetic imperfections are present, but nothing that affects functionality. Overall a reliable, well-maintained vehicle.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good, well-maintained condition at a fair and honest price. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint holds its color and shine nicely, though you'll notice a few minor scratches and light surface blemishes consistent with normal everyday use. There are no significant dents or structural concerns. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing moderate wear on the seats and high-touch surfaces, but nothing that detracts from daily usability. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been properly serviced; all major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and cooling \u2014 are in good working order. This is a solid, dependable vehicle for a buyer looking for honest value without the premium price tag of a mint-condition car.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This used vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and represents a solid choice for a buyer seeking dependable everyday transportation. The exterior presents well overall, with only the expected minor scuffs and light surface wear you'd anticipate from a vehicle that has seen regular use \u2014 no major dents, deep scratches, or rust concerns. The paint retains a reasonable shine and the body panels are straight and intact. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional; the upholstery shows modest wear on the driver's seat and high-touch areas, but there are no tears, stains, or broken components. All primary controls, windows, locks, and climate systems operate as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and consistently, with no warning lights present and no unusual noises or leaks observed. The vehicle has been kept up with routine maintenance and is ready to drive without any immediate repair needs. This is an honest, no-surprises listing for a buyer who wants a reliable used car at a fair price.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "terse_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "terse_4",
      "description": "This car is in good condition \u2014 well-maintained with minor cosmetic wear but mechanically sound and ready to drive.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
